NCS (Namaste Consultancy Services) wants to award employees based on number of projects completed by each individual each month.  
Write an SQL to find best employee for each month along with number of projects completed by him/her in that month.

Table: projects(primary key : project_id)

column name	             data type 
project id	             int
employee_name  	         varchar(20)
project_completion_date	 date

Example Input

projects

project_id	       employee_name	   project_completion_date
101	               Shilpa	           2023-01-03
102	               Shilpa	           2023-01-15
103	               Shilpa	           2023-01-22
104	               Rahul	           2023-01-05


Expected Output:

employee_name	      no_of_completed_projects
Shilpa	                      3
